Hartmann Incontinence



    Hartmann Incontinence

Moli disposable continence care products from Hartmann offers a comprehensive range of solutions to meet all types of incontinence problems.The discreet colour coding system helps you to select products of the correct absorbency level at a glance.With the premium range of Moli products, reliable performance and active skin protection are guaranteed. UK mainland delivery on orders over £45 are free - simply order online or call us on FREEPHONE 0800 035 3588. 



MoliCare Mobile



MoliCare Soft 



MoliCare Super Plus



MoliMed Comfort



MoliForm Premium Soft



MoliForm for Men



MoliMed for Men



MoliPants



MoliNea Rectangular Pads



MoliNea Couche



Strampelpeter



Keeps Skin Healthy with Active Skin Protection
Convincingly Safe
The three-part absorbent core of the Moli range ensures fluids are guided quickly into the super absorbent layer, locking both urine and odours safely inside.
Supreme Leakage Protection
Soft, non-woven inner cuffs provide reliable leakage protection.
The MoliForm® soft range of shaped pads features a unique Advanced Dry Zone for 30% more dryness*. This helps to promote healthy skin and provides maximum comfort for patients.
Active Skin Protection
Dermatologically tested and hypoallergenic, the Moli range helps to support the skin’s natural pH value of 5.5. Active Skin Protection is enhanced by using the Menalind professional Skin Care range from HARTMANN.
Maintaining Patient Dignity
Advanced technology allows the production of thin Continence Care products without compromising absorption capacity. The discreet, white textile-like backsheet material of the Moli products increases patients’ dignity and quality of life. HARTMANN products are supplied in discreet outer cartons.






